task.summary: Default task
Adds JSON and PNG files for the zombie woodcutter.
Adds the PNG/JSON files for the game's UI. Adds the game's UI to the LevelView.
Removes unnecessary draw function.
Adds Settings.json to gitignore.
Comitting Settings.json.
Updates IntelliJ settings.
Changes the order of draw calls, so the UI is drawn on top of the game.
Adds minimap drawing to the draw function.
Adds a cache for recently loaded sprite atlases.
Adds a cache for recently loaded sprite atlases.
Adds damage reduction for defending targets.
Adds check for null map tiles to pathfinding code.
Adds check to stop pathfinding/movement if no enemies are nearby.
Adds the clearPath function.
Adds code to draw minimap enemies. Randomized enemy spawning for testing.
Adds the button hover/press sfx.
Removes the button sound effects.
Adds a check to the setState function, so that it doesn't re-set a state that the button is already in. Adds debug code to draw a border around the button's bounding box.
Changes the order of checks in the constructPath function.
Increases the size of the "Weapon" bounding boxes of all entities.
Adds the new intro video.
Simplifies sections of the playVideo function and adds ESC functionality to skip the video.
Fixes a collision detection issue, where entities would often get stuck in room walls.
Adds a setter to the color instance variable.
Adds setters for the x/y axis position.
Updated the Deneane font to include characters required for the radio buttons.
Fixed an issue where the added characters couldn't be used.
Removes the settings file from git.
Adds color to the rarity enum.
Fixes minor performance in the draw function.
Removes all traces of the non-equipment inventory from the Inventory class.
Adds an inventory to the player.
Adds a getLabel function.
Adjust the size of the labels returned by the getLabel function.
Adds the Equip/Unequip buttons.
Adds the Equipment/ItemGenerator classes.
Moves inventory instance variable from player class to entity class.
Comitting everything.
